     <h3>
      Welcome to Keepsakes, Pitlochry, Scotland
     </h3>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Keepsakes
      </strong>
       is one of the most popular gift shops in
picturesque Pitlochry and is well known for the great selection and wide range
of gifts on offer - many of which can't be found in city shops. The choice
range of 
      <a href="giftsforhim/index.htm">
       gifts
      </a>
       is ever changing
as the owners 
      <a href="aboutus/index.htm">
       David Litterick and Lynda
Hudda
      </a>
      continuously search for items which are new and different.
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Keepsakes
      </strong>
       has built up a loyal customer base over the
years, and they are regularly heard to comment:-
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       <em>
        "A Lovely Shop"
       </em>
      </strong>
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       <em>
        “You have some beautiful things here”
       </em>
      </strong>
     </p>
     <p>
      <em>
       <strong>
        "A Great Selection of Unusual Gifts"
       </strong>
      </em>
     </p>
     <p>
      <em>
       <strong>
        "We Don't Find Shops Like This in The City"
       </strong>
      </em>
     </p>
     <p>
      <em>
       <strong>
        "We Always Find Something to Buy Here"
       </strong>
      </em>
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Keepsakes
      </strong>
       offers a wide range of gifts for every
occasion to suit all tastes and budgets and appeals to visitors and locals
alike.
     </p>
     <p>
      Don't just take our word for it - when you 
      <a href="contactus/index.htm">
       visit Pitlochry
      </a>
       call in to Keepsakes and decide
for yourself, we guarantee you won't be disappointed!
     </p>
